<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gripe1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gripe,</orth> subst. 1) a griffin: <cit><quote>a white hind under the --'s sharp claws,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 543" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 543</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) grasp, seizure: <bibl n="shak. h5 4.6.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 6, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.100" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 100</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.1.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 1, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 106</bibl> (cf. the verb in <bibl n="shak. h8 2.2.136" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 2, 136</bibl>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>